<p>As we near the end of this sequence, here's Ms. Sweetie, my second direct contribution to the series.</p>
<p><strong>Important Note:</strong> Credit to <strong>TroyL</strong> for the original idea. The central idea - what happened between Ms. Sweetie and Mr. Redd - is all his. (And that includes the use of that idea in the other Little Mister series, so it's important to point out!)</p>
<p>The writing, characterization, and the implied Xanatos Gambit, are mine. Any problems and issues and any bad writing are also all mine.</p>
<p>As always, be brutal, and be sure to tell me if you like it, too.</p>

