						<a class="title" href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,1940508)"></a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djoric" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(388108); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=388108&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610163639" alt="Djoric" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=388108)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djoric" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(388108); return false;" >Djoric</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1390194969 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">20 Jan 2014 05:16</span>
		</div>
